				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$^{\circ }\hbox {C}$$\end{document} for 20 minutes20, and emergence was recorded every two days.

For seedling growth assessments, the following traits were measured: Shoot Dry Mass (SDM) (g), Total Dry Mass (TDM) (g), Dickson’s Quality Index (DQI)21, Leaf Area (LA) (\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
