				\begin{document}$$F_{v}/F_{m}$$\end{document}), residual effects had a more pronounced impact on phenotypic expression. Consequently, heritability (\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
