				\begin{document}$$N_m$$\end{document}) of 14.75. All evaluated loci exhibited high polymorphic information content (PIC \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
